'From Squeak 2.3 beta of Nov 25, 1998 on 10 January 1999 at 1:47:19 pm'!"Change Set:		BBLineFailFixDate:			10 January 1999Author:			Dan IngallsFixes a possible stack imbalance error when primitive line drawing failed."!!Interpreter methodsFor: 'I/O primitives' stamp: 'di 1/10/1999 12:54'!primitiveDrawLoop	"Invoke the line drawing primitive."	| rcvr xDelta yDelta |	rcvr _ self stackValue: 2.	xDelta _ self stackIntegerValue: 1.	yDelta _ self stackIntegerValue: 0.	self success: (self loadBitBltFrom: rcvr).	successFlag ifTrue:		[self drawLoopX: xDelta Y: yDelta.		self showDisplayBits].	successFlag ifTrue:		[self pop: 2].! !